fields.quote: There’s something about arriving in new cities, wandering empty streets with no destination. I will never lose the love for the arriving, but I'm born to leave.-Charlotte Eriksson, Empty Roads & Broken Bottles
A city isn’t so unlike a person. They both have the marks to show they have many stories to tell. They see many faces. They tear things down and make new again.― Rasmenia Massoud, Broken Abroad
